- I rebooted the system
- I checked the logs (see and excerpt below). There are many similar messages about the plugin not working. **Is there any plugin specific log?**
- I also had a look into the database (postgres) and nothing "looked" wrong. However I noticed that there are many instances of `card_properties` share the same ID (due to templates?). Is this expected behaviour?

